1
00:00:00,370 --> 00:00:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Wanting to touch the waxing 
and waning moon</i></font>

2
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I reached out</i></font>

3
00:00:07,530 --> 00:00:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if it was a small, 
insignificant step</i></font>

4
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I traveled my universe</i></font>

5
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Believing I'll get there someday</i></font>

6
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Once one person stopped, 
more and more did.</i></font>

7
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People are gathering around my voice.</i></font>

8
00:00:23,180 --> 00:00:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

9
00:00:24,170 --> 00:00:28,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if I must walk down 
a path never trodden before</i></font>

10
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm actually being a singer.</i></font>

11
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if I'm dreaming too big, 
hoping for too much</i></font>

12
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's loosened up completely.</i></font>

13
00:00:31,150 --> 00:00:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is perfect.</i></font>

14
00:00:32,950 --> 00:00:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she can keep 
the audience here till the end,</i></font>

15
00:00:33,380 --> 00:00:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My hand traverses 
a 60 centimeter universe</i></font>

16
00:00:35,910 --> 00:00:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this should be a success, 
and her CD should sell.</i></font>

17
00:00:38,110 --> 00:00:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And gets closer to 
the bright side of the moon</i></font>

18
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Watch me</i></font>

19
00:00:51,550 --> 00:00:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}See?</i></font>

20
00:00:52,990 --> 00:00:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that logo...</font>

21
00:00:54,910 --> 00:00:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was "ask for the moon."</font>

22
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should get going.</font>

23
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Gimme a sec.</font>

24
00:01:19,810 --> 00:01:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take one copy of your CD.</font>

25
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'd like one as well.</font>

26
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

27
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you so much.</font>

28
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wow, there's so many people.</i></font>

29
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so strange.</i></font>

30
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The moment I stopped singing 
for lots of people,</i></font>

31
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>lots of people came forward 
to listen to me.</i></font>

32
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now for my third song, "Half & Half."</font>

33
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was worried at first, but now 
I'm glad I put on this show.</i></font>

34
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I hate the sound of drums.</font>

35
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:14,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you maybe, like, not play?</font>

36
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be ridiculous.</font>

37
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. So, uh, hello.</font>

38
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're Celestial.</font>

39
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nearly the first anniversary 
of our debut,</font>

40
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we're doing a surprise show 
in a memorable place.</font>

41
00:02:27,090 --> 00:02:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I wanted to.</font>

42
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! They're doing a homecoming 
concert here today?!</font>

43
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, isn't that Celestial?</font>

44
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, it's really them!</font>

45
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Hizu-chan!</font>

46
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're performing here again?</font>

47
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is crazy.</font>

48
00:02:38,950 --> 00:02:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

49
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

50
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:47,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like the universe is out 
to get me or something.</font>

51
00:02:48,690 --> 00:02:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}INOHANA RIKKA</font>

52
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first song is...</font>

53
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it have a title?</font>

54
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It does! You came up with it!</font>

55
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

56
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, here we go.</font>

57
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're popping a throat drop now?</font>

58
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just let her be.</font>

59
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go with our first song.</font>

60
00:04:48,770 --> 00:04:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One, two...</font>

61
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How does a three-piece band 
have such intensity?</i></font>

62
00:04:57,740 --> 00:05:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Give me the impulse!</i></font>

63
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:05,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I've traveled a long, long time</i></font>

64
00:05:05,930 --> 00:05:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Through a darkness 
that drowned out my voice</i></font>

65
00:05:12,710 --> 00:05:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Walking on and on, 
as if to find the next stretch</i></font>

66
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That vocalist is insanely good!</i></font>

67
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Of this lonely, lonely thread</i></font>

68
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My voice is buried, down and out</i></font>

69
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}So I'll drag it out and shout</i></font>

70
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You only get one flicker, 
shut everything out</i></font>

71
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You only get one shot, 
blaze a trail and hit your mark</i></font>

72
00:05:42,910 --> 00:05:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You only get one life, 
what will you choose?</i></font>

73
00:05:48,570 --> 00:05:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Make your heart beat 
in the moment, let it shine!</i></font>

74
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Urp. Whoops, I just burped.</font>

75
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I felt I was all alone</i></font>

76
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>O...</i></font>

77
00:06:04,710 --> 00:06:06,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Okay, here's my third song,</i></font>

78
00:06:06,530 --> 00:06:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I failed to even come into my own</i></font>

79
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"Half and Half."</i></font>

80
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It all, all comes to end, like it or not</i></font>

81
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Then take in the now, now</i></font>

82
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}If your voice was shut off 
and locked away</i></font>

83
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Unleash it and shout</i></font>

84
00:06:31,770 --> 00:06:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You only get one flicker, 
gather it all up</i></font>

85
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:41,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You only get one shot, 
blaze a trail and rend the sky</i></font>

86
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:41,300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hey, what is this feeling?</i></font>

87
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We only have one life, 
and that's what we'll choose</i></font>

88
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:44,140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Acting like I'm clueless</i></font>

89
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rikka's doing great.</i></font>

90
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:46,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But deep down, I know</i></font>

91
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her voice sounds way better 
than it did in the first song.</i></font>

92
00:06:46,590 --> 00:06:50,960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Because it's obvious</i></font>

93
00:06:46,930 --> 00:06:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Make your heart beat 
in the moment, let it shine!</i></font>

94
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's doing nothing wrong!</i></font>

95
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And yet, this had to happen.</i></font>

96
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:57,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>My world's glittering like 
a page out of a shoujo manga</i></font>

97
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Rikka's not to blame here.</i></font>

98
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's my fault for picking this spot!</i></font>

99
00:06:58,890 --> 00:07:05,320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I don't need confidence or reassurance</i></font>

100
00:07:03,410 --> 00:07:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, become a musician with me.</i></font>

101
00:07:07,410 --> 00:07:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aiko was the one 
who asked me to join her.</i></font>

102
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, why'd you ask me 
to team up with you?</font>

103
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of your voice, duh.</font>

104
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was love at first listen.</font>

105
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew your voice was a real moneymaker.</font>

106
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Money? Seriously?</font>

107
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had one more reason.</font>

108
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the type to get front-row tickets 
for my favorite singer's shows.</font>

109
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

110
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know,</font>

111
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">standing next to you is like 
being in your front row.</font>

112
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hear your voice 
from as close as possible.</font>

113
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

114
00:07:42,050 --> 00:07:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Together, we wrote a song 
called "In the Calm of Night,"</i></font>

115
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and sent the finished version 
to a record label.</i></font>

116
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}"IN THE CALM OF NIGHT"</font>

117
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, they sent a message!</font>

118
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They want to meet us in person!</font>

119
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

120
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Man, those were the days.</i></font>

121
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one of you sang the chorus?</font>

122
00:08:02,990 --> 00:08:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only need that girl's voice.</font>

123
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

124
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't do this! We worked together—</font>

125
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka.</font>

126
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy for you.</font>

127
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best for me too, okay?</font>

128
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She must've had so much to say back then.</i></font>

129
00:08:21,930 --> 00:08:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll lock it all up for now and run</i></font>

130
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:29,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She hid them all behind her smile 
and supported me,</i></font>

131
00:08:28,190 --> 00:08:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}To where I can hear your voice 
and you can hear mine</i></font>

132
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I ran away because of one setback.</i></font>

133
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With each sway of my hair, 
I get one step closer</i></font>

134
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I stayed in my comfort zone,</i></font>

135
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>sang other people's songs 
to be fake popular,</i></font>

136
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I can hear my panting and my heartbeat</i></font>

137
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and acted like I hadn't 
given up on music.</i></font>

138
00:08:43,590 --> 00:08:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No wonder she got mad at me.</i></font>

139
00:08:44,490 --> 00:08:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It must be because I ran so hard</i></font>

140
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}What should I say first?</i></font>

141
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just decided to stop singing 
for the masses, but this still stings.</i></font>

142
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Something that's like me 
to say, from me to you</i></font>

143
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh no. If I keep looking down, 
I might actually cry.</i></font>

144
00:08:57,610 --> 00:09:01,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I kept thinking all this while...</i></font>

145
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:59,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I just can't look up...</i></font>

146
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hey! What are you doing, Yamabuki-kun?</i></font>

147
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, if you're having a hard time 
and can't keep your head up,</font>

148
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">look in my eyes and nowhere else.</font>

149
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:14,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made the right call in bringing these.</font>

150
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could see me 
even with your teary eyes, huh?</font>

151
00:09:19,850 --> 00:09:22,600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>And I told you I'd die of cringe...</i></font>

152
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Rikka?</font>

153
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really want it to end this way?</font>

154
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't you going to sing 
for the person dear to you?!</font>

155
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you just going to 
let your dream die here?!</font>

156
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Did you ask her to come?</i></font>

157
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I...</font>

158
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was handing out fliers by the station.</font>

159
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}INOHANA RIKKA
STREET PERFORMANCE</font>

160
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't expect her to show up now.</i></font>

161
00:09:47,170 --> 00:09:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm glad I handed it to her just in case.</i></font>

162
00:09:57,180 --> 00:10:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aiko, I... I'm sorry!</font>

163
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sing.</font>

164
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came here to listen to you sing.</font>

165
00:10:06,530 --> 00:10:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've never been talkative 
or had a way with words.</font>

166
00:10:10,330 --> 00:10:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's easier for me to know 
what you want if you just sing.</font>

167
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

168
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

169
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This will be my last number.</i></font>

170
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:26,540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I wrote this song for my best friend.</i></font>

171
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>This is "trails."</i></font>

172
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We're walking towards the rainbow, 
you said with a smile</i></font>

173
00:10:55,720 --> 00:11:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a smile that shined 
like a glass marble</i></font>

174
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}So I packed everything I could think of</i></font>

175
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In this old backpack of mine</i></font>

176
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We can go wherever we want, 
as far as we want</i></font>

177
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until our hands touch 
the base of the rainbow</i></font>

178
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let's go see things never seen before</i></font>

179
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until we wave goodbye 
at the crossroads someday</i></font>

180
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:45,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until we wave goodbye 
under the rainbow someday</i></font>

181
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you think?</font>

182
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good enough.</font>

183
00:12:09,070 --> 00:12:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

184
00:12:09,710 --> 00:12:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's the encore?</font>

185
00:12:11,170 --> 00:12:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Encore? But I only wrote four new songs.</font>

186
00:12:21,210 --> 00:12:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting tired of this, 
so can we call it a day?</font>

187
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I guess?</font>

188
00:12:26,570 --> 00:12:28,080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hey!</i></font>

189
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:30,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Listen up, you sheeple!</i></font>

190
00:12:30,530 --> 00:12:33,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Rikka's gonna sing 
"In the Calm of Night"! Listen!</i></font>

191
00:12:33,290 --> 00:12:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What are you doing?!</font>

192
00:12:35,350 --> 00:12:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lay off me. Those guys piss me off.</font>

193
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why "In the Calm of Night"?</font>

194
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, did you forget it?</font>

195
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I could ever...</font>

196
00:12:44,010 --> 00:12:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-They picked a fight with us! So scary!</font>

197
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do they want a battle?</font>

198
00:12:49,850 --> 00:12:52,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What, you scared of battling us?</i></font>

199
00:12:52,350 --> 00:12:55,430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Bring it, you cowards.</i></font>

200
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aiko, quit provoking them.</font>

201
00:12:57,230 --> 00:13:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek! I-I don't have any money on me!</font>

202
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare they mock us. 
Let's go, Hizumi!</font>

203
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's time for a battle of the bands!</i></font>

204
00:13:04,610 --> 00:13:06,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Are you ready?</i></font>

205
00:13:04,610 --> 00:13:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Y-Yamabuki-kun, stop Aiko!</font>

206
00:13:06,970 --> 00:13:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are your balls, Celestial?!</font>

207
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamabuki-kun?!</font>

208
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:13,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to show off here 
and make yourself memorable!</font>

209
00:13:13,540 --> 00:13:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But...</font>

210
00:13:15,340 --> 00:13:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The spectators are all over there.</font>

211
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:20,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It don't matter. Listen up.</i></font>

212
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:22,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Here's "In the Calm of Night," 
special arrangement.</i></font>

213
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:26,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arrangement?</font>

214
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, get to it.</font>

215
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, you're always so bossy.</font>

216
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Aiko. I'm sorry for everything.</font>

217
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for everything, too.</font>

218
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I gotten any better at singing?</font>

219
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

220
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meanie.</font>

221
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How am I supposed to tell 
with just one song?</font>

222
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll listen again, but this time...</font>

223
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As the sun sank into the sea</i></font>

224
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We let out a deep sigh</i></font>

225
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And the oceans responded to us</i></font>

226
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a big white wave</i></font>

227
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And dragged the wind away with it</i></font>

228
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}After we saw it off</i></font>

229
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We made a promise for no reason</i></font>

230
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The calm takes over the night</i></font>

231
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When the calm takes over the night</i></font>

232
00:14:53,310 --> 00:15:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We feel like there's nobody else 
in the world but us</i></font>

233
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The sea blends into the sky</i></font>

234
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When the sea quietly blends into the sky</i></font>

235
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I know it's just the two of us</i></font>

236
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But I still whisper to you</i></font>

237
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Ah, ah, in the calm of night</i></font>

238
00:15:28,950 --> 00:15:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}IN RIKKA'S FRONT ROW</font>

239
00:15:33,660 --> 00:15:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

240
00:15:34,430 --> 00:15:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready? Cheers to a good concert!</font>

241
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers to that!</font>

242
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Way to go-Iko!</font>

243
00:15:39,220 --> 00:15:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your show was great, Rikka-chan.</font>

244
00:15:41,310 --> 00:15:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just happened to be there, okay? 
By sheer luck.</font>

245
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, a total coincidence. 
Miracles are real, huh?</font>

246
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

247
00:15:49,810 --> 00:15:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try to be less obvious.</font>

248
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even managed to sell 
more than 20 copies of your CD.</font>

249
00:15:54,310 --> 00:15:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a huge success.</font>

250
00:15:55,740 --> 00:15:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My quota was 50 copies, though.</font>

251
00:15:58,300 --> 00:16:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, not bad for a first time, I guess.</font>

252
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You did good.</font>

253
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've invited 
Aiko-chan to join us, too.</font>

254
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, I tried, okay?</font>

255
00:16:08,950 --> 00:16:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell nah! I'm too shy for that!</font>

256
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meeting new people is too much for me!</font>

257
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:15,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has all that fire 
and she's a shy girl?</font>

258
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just have a private party 
with her later.</font>

259
00:16:18,430 --> 00:16:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you managed to patch things up.</font>

260
00:16:25,850 --> 00:16:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, yikes!</font>

261
00:16:27,290 --> 00:16:29,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I left my wallet in the park!</font>

262
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

263
00:16:30,210 --> 00:16:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go get it!</font>

264
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a cliché.</font>

265
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it, though?</font>

266
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want us to go with you?</font>

267
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nah. It's fine.</font>

268
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:41,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, Errand Boy! Get going!</font>

269
00:16:41,140 --> 00:16:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go with her and do everything 
in your power to help!</font>

270
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:47,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you at school the day after tomorrow.</font>

271
00:16:47,430 --> 00:16:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bucky, you'd better not 
do anything weird, okay?</font>

272
00:16:50,090 --> 00:16:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye, Rikka!</font>

273
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, weird?</font>

274
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, the whole car to ourselves.</font>

275
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucky me, 'cause my legs are beat.</font>

276
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, look.</font>

277
00:17:05,190 --> 00:17:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sun's setting over the sea. 
It's beautiful.</font>

278
00:17:09,370 --> 00:17:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you take a seat, too?</font>

279
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yours truly remains unseated wherever 
possible for my lower body health.</font>

280
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

281
00:17:17,870 --> 00:17:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you had the prime seat 
next to me available, too.</font>

282
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you always miss these chances?</font>

283
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be fine if it was 
delivered to lost-and-found,</font>

284
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but where would we look 
for it if it wasn't?</font>

285
00:17:28,860 --> 00:17:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's even more worried 
about my wallet than me.</i></font>

286
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was nerve-racking, but I had fun.</font>

287
00:17:36,650 --> 00:17:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My heart is still racing.</font>

288
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a good show.</font>

289
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did well seeing it through.</font>

290
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I didn't manage to sell 50 CDs,</font>

291
00:17:46,610 --> 00:17:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm still satisfied.</font>

292
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so hot.</font>

293
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I managed to write some good songs, too.</font>

294
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought giving up on mass appeal 
to sing for the people I want to reach</font>

295
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would be this fun.</font>

296
00:18:02,860 --> 00:18:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think I picked the wrong approach.</font>

297
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

298
00:18:11,650 --> 00:18:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

299
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I really not choose wrong?</font>

300
00:18:16,630 --> 00:18:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course you didn't.</font>

301
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:21,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to have fun before anything else.</font>

302
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did have fun</font>

303
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">until the middle.</font>

304
00:18:24,930 --> 00:18:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when the audience 
I'd attracted left me,</font>

305
00:18:29,650 --> 00:18:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt bitter, sad, and really miserable.</font>

306
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can say I only sing for 
certain people all I want,</font>

307
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it still stings when the audience 
abandons me like that.</font>

308
00:18:41,950 --> 00:18:43,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't your fault!</font>

309
00:18:43,820 --> 00:18:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Celestial just happened 
to do a show nearby!</font>

310
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All it means is that they had my number.</font>

311
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Music is about popularity, and 
we're fighting over the same fans.</font>

312
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what it means to live as a pro.</font>

313
00:18:59,090 --> 00:19:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you'd be up for it.</font>

314
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I expected too much of you.</font>

315
00:19:06,130 --> 00:19:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

316
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, hello. I'm almost at the office.</font>

317
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it went great.</font>

318
00:19:12,760 --> 00:19:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}INOHANA RIKKA
STREET PERFORMANCE</font>

319
00:19:13,140 --> 00:19:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you hate rabbits?</font>

320
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Celestial's show went over great.</font>

321
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's trending on socials, too.</font>

322
00:19:20,230 --> 00:19:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, also, there was a high 
schooler performing nearby.</font>

323
00:19:24,370 --> 00:19:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was kinda interesting.</font>

324
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a peace sign, not a rabbit.</font>

325
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}INOHANA RIKKA
STREET PERFORMANCE</font>

326
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what does this mean?</font>

327
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thinking of reaching out to her.</font>

328
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

329
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A SYMBOL FOR DEFIANCE</font>

330
00:19:39,990 --> 00:19:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if Rikka-chan found her wallet.</font>

331
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The errand boy will take care of it.</font>

332
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you actually trust him.</font>

333
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? It's not like that.</font>

334
00:19:48,490 --> 00:19:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I guess he is handy to have around.</font>

335
00:19:51,570 --> 00:19:54,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm having him do so much for me.</font>

336
00:19:54,650 --> 00:19:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell!</font>

337
00:19:55,770 --> 00:19:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you run away!</font>

338
00:19:58,870 --> 00:20:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iko-chan's so tough.</font>

339
00:20:00,690 --> 00:20:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that mean?</font>

340
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I've got stuff to do, too.</font>

341
00:20:04,130 --> 00:20:05,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

342
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bye.</font>

343
00:20:06,330 --> 00:20:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

344
00:20:16,370 --> 00:20:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to think I chose wrong.</font>

345
00:20:20,890 --> 00:20:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But maybe everything I've been saying</font>

346
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is just an excuse to run away 
from the competition?</font>

347
00:20:28,570 --> 00:20:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka...</font>

348
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I really keep 
pursuing music like this?</font>

349
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

350
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you crying?</font>

351
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me. I deserve the blame.</font>

352
00:20:48,330 --> 00:20:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

353
00:20:49,420 --> 00:20:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should've known there was a chance 
Celestial would show up there.</font>

354
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I had researched more thoroughly...</font>

355
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did nothing wrong!</font>

356
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your songs, your vocals... 
They were all good!</font>

357
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all my fault!</font>

358
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop that.</font>

359
00:21:04,590 --> 00:21:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted this show to become 
a fun memory for you, and yet...</font>

360
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're blaming yourself too much.</font>

361
00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody could've seen that coming.</font>

362
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The next stop is Kaihin-Makuhari.</i></font>

363
00:21:16,470 --> 00:21:17,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh no!</font>

364
00:21:17,650 --> 00:21:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Now arriving at Kaihin-Makuhari.</i></font>

365
00:21:17,650 --> 00:21:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

366
00:21:18,630 --> 00:21:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a Yamabuki! Nobody can see my tears!</font>

367
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you, famous?</font>

368
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never know who's watching and where!</font>

369
00:21:27,040 --> 00:21:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you deface your name, 
fixing it is difficult!</font>

370
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeesh. What am I to do with you?</font>

371
00:21:29,670 --> 00:21:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The train on platform number one 
is a local train for Soga.</i></font>

372
00:21:36,420 --> 00:21:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check out the lovebirds.</font>

373
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to be young.</font>

374
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: SRIRAM GURUNATHAN
TIMING: MARIANA MARTINEZ
EDITING: WILLIAM HAGGARD</font>

375
00:22:05,740 --> 00:22:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You went above and beyond 
for me, Yamabuki-kun.</font>

376
00:22:05,760 --> 00:22:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CHECK: S BILYEU
TRANSLATION CHECK: MICHELLE TYMON</font>

377
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rest was up to me.</font>

378
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I suck so bad.</font>

379
00:22:14,910 --> 00:22:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do not.</font>

380
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Compared to Celestial, I do.</font>

381
00:22:18,790 --> 00:22:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you showed more heart.</font>

382
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love your music more.</font>

383
00:22:26,260 --> 00:22:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure that's an opinion 
my producer should have?</font>

384
00:22:30,370 --> 00:22:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Showing more heart
doesn't mean it'll resonate.</font>

385
00:22:32,740 --> 00:22:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just pretty, idealistic nonsense.</font>

386
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it?</font>

387
00:22:36,170 --> 00:22:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is.</font>

388
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:50,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}ANCHORING 101</font>

389
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}VOICE ACTRESS PERSONALITY QUIZ!!</font>

390
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So very pretty.</font>

